OL,7,FRegular blood tests will monitor their
OL,8,Flevels of PFAS until they are deemed
OL,9,Fsafe.
OL,11,FA clinical service to manage PFAS
OL,12,Finterventions will be available to
OL,13,Fislanders later this year.
OL,15,FThe government will also begin testing
OL,16,Fpeople previously untested by Public
OL,17,FHealth three years ago.
