OL,7,FThose who may have been exposed to
OL,8,FPFAS through work, for example,
OL,9,Ffirefighters involved in the clean up
OL,10,Fwill be offered accredited blood
OL,11,Ftesting by the government.
OL,13,FFurther testing will also be offered
OL,14,Fto residents who lived in the extended
OL,15,F'plume' area and drank from the
OL,16,Fprivate water supply for at least one
OL,17,Fyear since 1991.
