OL,7,FDeputy Tom Binet says: "People who've
OL,8,Flived in the plume area have been
OL,9,Fsubjected to drinking water that's
OL,10,Fvery high in PFAS, and I think we all
OL,11,Fagree that it makes perfect sense to
OL,12,Ftry and do something to reduce those
OL,13,FPFAS levels.
OL,15,F"We've got to, at this point in time,
OL,16,Fbe dealing with the people that have
OL,17,Fbeen subjected to high levels of PFAS
OL,18,F(and) get the best treatment that we
OL,19,Fcan provide them.
