OL,4,Creduce 'forever chemicals' in their
OL,5,Cblood
OL,7,F"PFAS is prevalent everywhere, but I
OL,8,Fthink we're ahead of the game. We're
OL,9,Finvesting a lot of money, time, and
OL,10,Feffort into the research.
OL,12,F"It's important to mention that the
OL,13,Festimates are that 20% of the PFAS in
OL,14,Four system comes from our water, so
OL,15,Fit's only part of the problem, and
OL,16,Fwe've got to have a proportionate
OL,17,Fapproach."
